<li><a href="https://pnpm.io/zh/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">pnpm</a> is used as the package manager, although npm or yarn is also supported;</li>
<li>VuePress is installed as a project dependency, and the following script is configured in <code v-pre>package.json</code>:</li>
</ul>
